OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FOne of the first lung transplant
OL,8,Fpatients to receive a skin patch from
OL,9,Ftheir donor, used to detect organ
OL,10,Frejection earlier, said the method
OL,11,Fhelped him get treatment faster.
OL,13,FDarren White was given steroids when
OL,14,Ftests confirmed his body was rejecting
OL,15,Fhis new lung three months after his
OL,16,Ftransplant.
OL,18,FMore than a year on, the 53-year-old
OL,19,Fis doing well and said he can be "more
OL,20,Fof a dad" to his toddler as he is able
OL,21,Fto walk and take him to the park.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FExperts leading the Sentinel trial
OL,8,Fsaid the skin patch, which is grafted
OL,9,Fonto the forearm of patients at the
OL,10,Fsame time as their lung transplant,
OL,11,Facts as a "window".
OL,13,FScientists believe the skin rejects
OL,14,Fearlier than other organs and is more
OL,15,Fvisible, meaning medics can treat
OL,16,Frejection as soon as a rash appears
OL,17,Fand slash the risk of permanent damage.
OL,19,FSo far, ten patients have received
OL,20,F10cm by 3cm skin patches from their
OL,21,Forgan donor as part of the study.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FMr White, a former bus driver from
OL,8,FStockton-on-Tees, had a lung
OL,9,Ftransplant in late 2024.
OL,11,FEarlier the same year, he was
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with lung fibrosis, which
OL,13,Fcauses the lungs to become scarred and
OL,14,Fmakes breathing difficult.
OL,16,FHe said he did not hesitate to say yes
OL,17,Fwhen approached about the trial while
OL,18,Fon the waiting list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,F"Anything that might help to avoid
OL,8,Frejection was worth a try," Mr White
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"Rejection is the biggest fear of any
OL,12,Ftransplant recipient, so having
OL,13,Fsomething that might be able to catch
OL,14,Fit much sooner than otherwise was
OL,15,Freally appealing," he added.
OL,17,FAccording to NHS Blood and Transplant
OL,18,F(NHSBT), lung rejection is hard to
OL,19,Fdetect as it can involve blood tests,
OL,20,Fbiopsies and X-rays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FRates of rejection are highest in the
OL,8,Ffirst three to six months post-
OL,9,Fsurgery, and happen in almost a third
OL,10,Fof patients.
OL,12,FThree months after having his
OL,13,Ftransplant, Mr White noticed a purple
OL,14,Frash on the skin patch and sent photos
OL,15,Fto medics.
OL,17,FA biopsy showed mild rejection, and he
OL,18,Fwas treated with steroids.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
