FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,F"I definitely believe the skin patch
OL,8,Fhelped to stop the lungs from being
OL,9,Frejected", Mr White said.
OL,11,F"I was feeling fine, there was no
OL,12,Freason for me to think that the lungs
OL,13,Fwere being rejected. The only sign was
OL,14,Fthe rash.
OL,16,F"I'm over a year post-transplant now
OL,17,Fand doing really well. Who knows if
OL,18,Fthat would be the case if the rash
OL,19,Fhadn't shown up and rejection wasn't
OL,20,Fspotted until further down the line."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FMr White, who is a father to Daniel,
OL,8,Fthree, said he hopes the trial shows
OL,9,Fskin patches are a viable way of
OL,10,Fdetecting organ rejection early.
OL,12,FSpeaking about life post-transplant,
OL,13,Fhe said: "The biggest difference is I
OL,14,Fcan walk, I can take Daniel to the
OL,15,Fpark to play. Before he could sit on
OL,16,Fmy knee, drive my buggy, but that was
OL,17,Fit, I couldn't do much with him. I can
OL,18,Fbe more of a dad now.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,F"My favourite thing is to go to the
OL,8,Fpark. Daniel always asks to go on the
OL,9,Fswing and we have one in our garden. I
OL,10,Fcan push him now. It's the simple
OL,11,Fthings that are the best, we both love
OL,12,Fit."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
