PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FThe Sentinel trial is set to run until
OL,8,F2027 and will recruit 152 patients at
OL,9,Ffive centres: Freeman Hospital,
OL,10,FHarefield Hospital, Queen Elizabeth
OL,11,FHospital, Royal Papworth and
OL,12,FWythenshawe Hospital.
OL,14,FThe skin grafts are carried out by
OL,15,Fplastic surgeons at the University of
OL,16,FOxford.
OL,18,FThe families of donors must consent
OL,19,Ffor the skin transplant to take place
OL,20,Fvia NHSBT specialist nurses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
