FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FHenk Giele, chief investigator of
OL,8,FSentinel and an Oxford plastic
OL,9,Fsurgeon, said: "It seems logical that
OL,10,Fhaving a window to your transplant can
OL,11,Fprovide an early warning system of
OL,12,Frejection or reassure you that you
OL,13,Fdon't have rejection but we have to
OL,14,Fprove it works.
OL,26,@qD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
