PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,F"We are so grateful to the patients,
OL,8,Fthe donors and their families, the
OL,9,Ftransplant teams, and the NHSBT staff
OL,10,Fwho make this important trial happen.
OL,11,FWe hope it will change what we know
OL,12,Fabout transplant and make patients'
OL,13,Flives better and longer."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
