OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775675472
OL,3,CPatient spotted his new lung was being
OL,4,Crejected thanks to skin graft from
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FEmma Lawson, organ donation innovation
OL,8,Fand research lead at NHSBT, added:
OL,9,F"Thanks to the generosity of amazing
OL,10,Fdonor families providing additional
OL,11,Fconsent for skin grafts, patients are
OL,12,Fnow receiving them, and we are
OL,13,Fprivileged to work alongside them to
OL,14,Fenable this important trial to go
OL,15,Fahead."
